  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together quinoa, chickpeas, kalamata olives, artichoke hearts, feta cheese, fresh parsley, lemon juice, olive oil, garlic, onion, cumin, and paprika",
    "Add gluten-free beer to the bowl and stir to combine",
    "Transfer the mixture to a pandan leaf wrap and shape into a log",
    "Bake for 25 minutes, or until the quinoa is tender and the flavors are melded together",
    "Let the brew bake rest for 5 minutes before slicing and serving"
